Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只有守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:53.80,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}才懂得憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}擁抱無名的悸動  只是脆弱的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}最終只能轟然潰去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:09.05,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}內心隱藏著野性的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:14.56,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}爭鬥慘劇  非己所望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:21.04,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只見希望之星已隕落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}悲慘的宿命在呐喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:29.34,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}「撕碎我吧  可愛的人兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}「快去攫取  那熹微的夢」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}然而呼喊只是夢幻泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:37.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}光明與祈禱變成了背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}只能接受那無情的裁罰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:45.67,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}笑靨俱往矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:52.26,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}唯有迷惘在晨曦
